Each pod is running some kind of service. 

We will create some kind of object in our cluster. 

This is an object called secreat. 

in Secreate we can create a key value pairs. 

Secreate will be exposed as Env Varaibles. 

These env varaible are the same pods of these services where they are running. 

We can easiy access those env varaibles which are inside those pods. 

We can run a command 
kubectl create secret generic jwt-secrete --from-literal=jwt=asdf

This is easy , but when every to you create or spin up a new cluster we need to remember the all secreats we created over time. 

Store this in some safe file. 